

Left Outer Join - 



Note - Humne Jo 2 New Tables Create Kiye h student_latest & courses_latest Usme se Humne Jo courses_latest Table Hain Usme se Course_id 2 ko Delete Kar diye Left Outer Join Dekhne k Liye Jiski Wajah se 3B Table k course_name Column me "NULL" dikh raha h Q ki Jo Course Tha wo Delete Ho Gya.


3) Inner Join In The New Tables Which We have Created 


A) SELECT student_latest.student_fname, student_latest.student_lname, courses_latest.course_name FROM student_latest JOIN courses_latest ON student_latest.selected_course = courses_latest.course_id;

