B) Left Outer Join In The New Tables Which We have Created


SELECT student_latest.student_fname, student_latest.student_lname, courses_latest.course_name FROM student_latest LEFT JOIN courses_latest ON student_latest.selected_course = courses_latest.course_id;

+---------------+---------------+--------------+
| student_fname | student_lname | course_name  |
+---------------+---------------+--------------+
| rohit         | sharma        | NULL         |
| shikhar       | dhawan        | big data     |
| rahul         | dravid        | devops       |
| virat         | kohli         | data science |
| kapil         | dev           | big data     |
| brain         | lara          | NULL         |
| carl          | hooper        | data science |
| saurabh       | ganguly       | devops       |
+---------------+---------------+--------------+





